-- Luxalpha investors take UBS to court in Luxembourg
-- 
-- Thu Mar 19, 2009 6:01am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/03/19/us-madoff-ubs-luxalpha-idUSTRE52I2KM20090319

 

 PARIS  (Reuters) - Investors who bought shares in the Luxalpha fund have taken Swiss bank UBS ( UBSN.VX ) to court over losses related to the Bernard Madoff fraud, the investors said in a statement on Thursday. 

 The investors said they had served summons on Thursday, dealing with UBS's role in the affair. They said they wanted UBS to compensate them fully for losses they suffered from the Madoff fraud. (Reporting by  Sudip Kar-Gupta , Editing by Marcel Michelson)